
# Bookstore MERN Stack Application 📚🛒

## 📌 Overview
A full-stack bookstore web application built using the MERN stack that allows users to browse, add, update, and manage books through a modern web interface.

## 🎯 Problem Statement
Traditional bookstore systems lack scalability and a seamless digital experience. This project provides a modern, scalable, and responsive web-based solution.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Frontend: React.js
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js
- Database: MongoDB
- Language: JavaScript
- Tools: Git, REST APIs

## ✨ Features
- Book listing and management
- CRUD operations
- RESTful API architecture
- Responsive frontend UI
- Scalable backend design

## ⚙️ Application Flow
User → React Frontend → Express API → MongoDB → Response

